  {
    "id": "gdmrp-0003",
    "correctOption": "B",
    "difficulty": "medium",
    "sourceYear": 2024,
    "en": {
      "question": "The ratio of milk to water in a mixture is 5 : 3. If 40 litres of water is added, the ratio becomes 5 : 7. Find the original quantity of milk.",
      "options": [
        "40 L",
        "50 L",
        "60 L",
        "75 L"
      ],
      "explanation": "Let milk = 5x, water = 3x. After adding: 5x / (3x+40) = 5/7. 35x = 15x + 200. 20x = 200, x = 10. Milk = 5 x 10 = 50 L."
    },
    "hi": {
      "question": "एक मिश्रण में दूध और पानी का अनुपात 5 : 3 है। यदि 40 लीटर पानी मिलाया जाए, तो अनुपात 5 : 7 हो जाता है। दूध की मूल मात्रा ज्ञात करें।",
      "options": [
        "40 L",
        "50 L",
        "60 L",
        "75 L"
      ],
      "explanation": "माना दूध = 5x, पानी = 3x। मिलाने के बाद: 5x / (3x+40) = 5/7। 35x = 15x + 200। 20x = 200, x = 10। दूध = 5 × 10 = 50 L।"
    }
  },
