        "12 L",
        "16 L",
        "20 L",
        "24 L"
      ],
      "explanation": "Milk = 7/10 x 80 = 56 L, water = 24 L. New ratio: 56/(24+x) = 7/5. 280 = 168 + 7x. 7x = 112, x = 16 L."
